        "latin": "Y\u0101 ayyuhan-nabiyyu j\u0101hidil-kuff\u0101ra wal-mun\u0101fiq\u012bna waglu\u1e93 \u2018alaihim, wa ma'w\u0101hum jahannam(u), wa bi'sal-ma\u1e63\u012br(u).",
